  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Armor imbued with this seal gains a +1 to AC and can apply its Damage reduction (if any) to one Medical Release damage type from the following list.<br />You cannot change this choice, once made;</p><ul><li><p>Acid Damage</p></li><li><p>Necrotic Damage</p></li><li><p>Poison Damage</p></li></ul><hr /><p>If the armor this seal is applied to has no innate Damage Reduction, then you instead apply half of its armor bonus as if it was Damage reduction to the chosen damage type.</p><p></p>",
